snippet.title: The Architect : Paris - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
👏 The Architect : Paris is soon out of Early Access ! 👏
🚀 Available on Steam, Epic Game Store and GOG !🚀 🔽

📌 Steam : https://store.steampowered.com/app/1525620/The_Architect_Paris/?beta=0
📌 Epic : https://www.epicgames.com/store/en-US/p/the-architect-paris
📌 GOG: https://www.gog.com/game/the_architect_paris

► Music by MADSUN - Awake (Instrumental) | Madsun Music, Allo Floride Publishing

🔔 Don't forget to subscribe to get the latest news and videos from the game !
